    Display results table

    f_display_results_table.Rd

    Outputs an interactive results table suitable for HTML documents and the app. .

    f_display_results_table(coin, type = "scores")

    Arguments

    coin

    COIN object, or list with first entry is the indicator metadata, second entry is the aggregation metadata

    type

    set type = "scores" or "ranks"

    Value

    a visualised data table
